Body: Description: Hello, we received instructions from your team on how to activate the license key for our Pingcastle tool. Unfortunately, after downloading the pingcastle package, I did not see the PingCastle.exe.config file where, according to your instructions, I should put the key. Can you please guide me how to do it?

Steps to Reproduce Updated: 1- Download PC package
2- Don't see the PingCastle.exe.config file
What We've Learned Updated: Customer Downloaded the PC package but is not able to see the PingCastle.exe.config file
Next Steps Updated: Wait for customer to send screenshot
